description: A macro expansion tag applied to an annotation property which can be expanded into a more detailed axiom.

example of usage:
ObjectProperty: RO???
Label: spatially disjoint from
Annotations: expand_assertion_to "DisjointClasses: (http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051 some ?X)  (http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051 some ?Y)"

label: expand assertion to
